  <description>
    <![CDATA[ Shows an example of a Workflow that publishes 2 external endpoints (that are just HTTPS URLs, rather than endpoints of internal Services launched and managed by ProActive).
Then, the template uses the Control Task template "wait_for_signals" to wait until the signal Terminate_Job is received to terminate the Job.
Note that the 2 external endpoints remain available on the Job even when it is terminated. ]]>
  </description>
